{
  "stem": "18056.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 225.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But with Uncle Max we ran, because he pushed me at that time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He kind of said, raus, you have to get away from here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we-- well, it wasn't really-- you see, they let us all out because the Americans came and bombed the train.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The reason they did, because parallel to us was a-- one of those anti-air-- [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- the Germans were shooting up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they were trying to shoot down to the Germans, and they hit our train.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They thought this was soldiers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we lost 185 people there that day that we buried in the-- in the-- in the area there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yeah, we have three mass graves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So this is how-- how it really happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I-- and-- and then when they said, come back, you all come back now, it's-- everything is clear, well, I ran away. 200 people ran away.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And out of those 200, I'm sure 180, 175 are alive-- were alive after-- after the war was over.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, of course, you know, it happened that we were able to go in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were carrying me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was-- I was pretty much shot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I weighed about 96 pounds, and I couldn't walk really anymore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was hanging on these two guys.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, please, go, go, go, run, because the Germans were shooting after us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Leave me here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They said, no, we're not going to leave you here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We're going to take you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so we walked into the first house, that house that I showed you the picture of, and we asked if we can have some water.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I-- I spoke.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So-- and they saw that it wasn't just water that we need.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
